description.en:
Tezilla, this is the action game you have been waiting for!
Tezilla Dev Team aims to develop a game on the Binance Smart Chain.

- Earn Tezilla while playing (Completing 3 levels without the destruction of your vessel)
- NFT is going to be implemented within the game.
- NFT Tezilla Diamond Box that included Random weaponry, vessels, Tezilla (web based)
- User to be able to play must purchase a Fuel pass Big Reward Levels

What can you do with Tezilla?

- Sell it on DEX.
- Buy Tezilla Diamond Box.
- Upgrade your Spaceship.
- Buy Spaceship.
